@startuml
title State machine model of an ATM

[*] --> Greeting

state Greeting
Greeting : do / display welcome message

state CardInserted
CardInserted : do / get card details

state PinChecking
PinChecking : do / check PIN

state IncorrectPIN
IncorrectPIN : do / allow retry

state InvalidCard
InvalidCard : do / keep card for security
IncorrectPIN : do / increase attempts count

state CardRetrieval
CardRetrieval : do / return card if canceled

PinChecking --> IncorrectPIN : Incorrect PIN entered
PinChecking --> InvalidCard : Invalid card or too many incorrect PIN attempts

IncorrectPIN --> Greeting : Retry PIN
InvalidCard --> CardRetrieval : Timeout

CardRetrieval --> Greeting : Wait for next user

Greeting --> CardInserted : Card inserted

state OptionsDisplay
OptionsDisplay : do / display available options

PinChecking --> OptionsDisplay : Correct PIN entered

OptionsDisplay : do / process selected request

@enduml
